CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 25, 1945, pg. 13, reads: "Champ, Runner-Up - For the past several months, a bitter billiard tournament has been in progress at the Centre Avenue YMCA. When the smoke of battle cleared, Wilbert Holloway was declared the winner.  Walter (Musty) Pollard was runner-up. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Wilbert Holloway and Walter Pollard holding cues, standing behind billiard table in Centre Avenue YMCA
